data.description: WELCOME HOME to this beautiful, updated charmer. This 2 bedroom, 1 bath has a formal dining plus an eat in kitchen which is spacious & bright with newer cabinetry, hardware, butcher block counter tops, backsplash, pantry & custom island. Mudroom & laundry off the kitchen with new tiled flooring. Updated bathroom, lighting & fixtures. Newer roof, windows, AC, plumbing & water heater. Original hardwood floors have been refinished. For your outside enjoyment you have 2 wonderful full covered porch areas, large, fenced backyard & 1 car garage/shed. COME CHECK OUT this wonderful home & would also make a great rental.
